title: Speaker Ryan dismisses Dems' success in tight Pennsylvania election
text:
Speaker Ryan dismisses Dems' success in tight Pennsylvania election 10:16pm IST - 01:15 
U.S. House Speaker Paul Ryan says Pennsylvania's race was tight because Democratic candidate Conor Lamb ran as a ''conservative'' and outraised his Republican challenger Rick Saccone. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
